rows.name: Everything seems to be in order.

Whatever happens in Superbia,
we still have our duty to perform here.

I hope my family back in
Superbia is okay.

It's at times like this that we
need to pull ourselves together and
do our part.

Ah... What will become
of Alst?
We can't let Iira use this again...

The Divine Beast weapons from Judicium...
They had terrifying power...

Everything's clear! No movement from
Invidia since then.

I hope we can find a good use
for this Judician technology.

I wonder if this Divine Beast weapon
could be used to save people...
Can our Divine Beast...can this world...even survive?
Listening to all this is exhausting...
